c=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f6d49b4162e75240fc0f9f98d79f792d9eabc73","tid":500481,"uid":19867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T11:29:17.000Z","msg":"inception你唔明啲咩?"},{"pid":"92ac70b4f4ebea15a138952c42f342d9fc9fbb8d","tid":500481,"uid":64571,"like":4,"dislike":4,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T12:20:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>inception你唔明啲咩?</blockquote><br />\n唔明有咩咁好睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n呢方面matrix+animatrix真係完勝<br />\n(inception打鬥嗰啲位真係睇到訓著...)<br />\n我諗缺乏深層探討人性係主因<br />\nnolan啲戲通常都有呢個問題<br />\n懶係好深層咁留低反思位<br />\n實際表達嘅嘢都比較平庸<br />\n例如套戲最後個陀螺<br />\n屌你老味停頂唔停都討論幾年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nnolan撚應該會追住我嚟咬<br />\n不如試下咬嘅同時留啲你認為好睇嘅非nolan電影名<br />\n睇睇係我問題定你問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"626e39825bee1bc186c57521e655a8024e605e1f","tid":500481,"uid":77788,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T12:35:39.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9043cf0767067f631cab35debb5899c99b8e41b1","tid":500481,"uid":32150,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T12:40:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5f95c52fd051a76ba59597f0b5e89733b6faf1f","tid":500481,"uid":64571,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T12:55:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>另外求哲學、神學高手講解一下matrix<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n睇埋animatrix更震撼<br />\n大陸豆瓣啲影評好撚正,可以睇睇<br />\n(盲反撚可以唔使理我)<br />\n佢地分析到得好深入立體<br />\n都係嗰句<br />\nmatrix同inception嘅分別係<br />\n前者係從人出發<br />\n而後者嚟講, 人只係佈景<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52d95babaa1f241c769615dded770832e4c8